OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMurky during
OL,6,Fthe evening and overnight, with a
OL,7,Flittle light rain and drizzle for a
OL,8,Ftime, easing later. Areas of low
OL,9,Fcloud, mist and fog persisting in
OL,10,Fplaces through to dawn.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA murky start, with cloud
OL,13,Fbreaks eventually developing to allow
OL,14,Flimited sunny intervals, most likely
OL,15,Fin then east. Cloudier in the west,
OL,16,Fwith light rain or drizzle for a time.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
