OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FMainly
OL,6,Ffine through this period, but with
OL,7,Fsome haziness and low cloud at times.
OL,8,Fbecoming breezier and eventually
OL,9,Fclearer through Tuesday. Temperatures
OL,10,Fa little above average by day and
OL,11,Fnight.
